---
title: Tuscan Sausage and Farro Soup with Herb Butter Toasts
description: During this time of year, we crave dinners that are hearty, rustic, and soul-warming. This soup checks all of those boxes. It has a tomatoey broth as its base that gets filled up with Italian chicken sausage, bites of carrot, aromatic herbs, and farro (that’s an ancient grain with a wholesome, nutty flavor). And because no soup is complete without some bread for dunking, we’re also throwing in some ciabatta toasts spread with herb butter.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tuscan-sausage-and-farro-soup-9b70e621.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/tuscan-sausage-and-farro-soup-5bb4d43dae08b57e3b6bed3b-a058a869.pdf
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/tuscan-sausage-and-farro-soup-5bb4d43dae08b57e3b6bed3b
servings: 2
author: HelloFresh
cuisine: Italian
time required: 40 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 720 kcal
  fat: 35 g
  saturated fat: 13 g
  carbohydrates: 62 g
  sugar: 9 g
